{"type": "article", "id": 11915, "title": "纯手工香水", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-10T11:30:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606004150XUEgl3zN2C4iITD1.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tEzra Woods 和 Alia Raza 是两位调香师，他们去年创办了自己的品牌 Régime des Fleurs，专门制作纯手工香水。他们认为香水应该是暧昧模糊的，不是图像，但可以传达图像的意味。今年他们推出的新系列香水选用的是绿松香，紫罗兰，木炭等，试图传达一个“倒映在池塘里的速写”的画面。<a href=\"http://regimedesfleurs.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261359028myPgSY4ZCXjpkz9.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261359032YxkUTN4zLHfWVFm.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072613590418ZwN3vJSebhtug2.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}